# No external contracts for this feature.
#
# Publisher-derived geographic recall adds no MCP tool and consumes no new
# data.egov.bg portal endpoint. It is an internal curation-side enrichment that
# implements the EXISTING `Extractor` interface (src/enrich/extractor.ts) and
# writes to the EXISTING `dataset_entities` table — no contract surface changes.
#
# Per Constitution III (Contract-First API Design), contract tests are required
# only for MCP tools and consumed portal endpoints; neither is introduced here,
# so there is no parity-matrix entry to add. This directory is intentionally
# empty (kept under version control via this .gitkeep).
